(6,'Home Testimonials','home_testimonials','<div data-content-type=\"html\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\">&lt;div class=\"testimonial-outer-wrapper slider-block top-margin bottom-margin\" style=\"background-image: url({{media url=\'wysiwyg/testimonial/eCom-background.jpg\'}});\"&gt;\r\n    &lt;div class=\"page-main\"&gt;\r\n        &lt;div class=\"title-block\"&gt;\r\n            &lt;strong&gt;\r\n                &lt;span&gt;What client say&lt;/span&gt;\r\n            &lt;/strong&gt;\r\n        &lt;/div&gt;\r\n        &lt;div class=\"testimonial-slider\"&gt;\r\n            &lt;div class=\"item\"&gt;                \r\n                &lt;div class=\"text-block\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p&gt;Special thanks to the team at Georg Jensen, so my old old bracelet can be fixed and stay with me for at least another 20 some years! (Perhaps the rest of my life.)\r\n\r\nThe entire experience was delightful. Service was professional and it didn’t take long to fix the bracelet actually.  :-)\r\n\r\nOne of the best brands in the world!!!\r\n                    &lt;/p&gt;                    \r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                &lt;div class=\"image-block\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;img src=\"{{media url=wysiwyg/testimonial/file_2.jpeg}}\" alt=\"\" /&gt;\r\n                    &lt;span class=\"testimonial-name\"&gt;David Lai&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                    &lt;span class=\"testimonial-desc\"&gt;Data Scientist&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n            &lt;/div&gt;\r\n            &lt;div class=\"item\"&gt;\r\n                &lt;div class=\"text-block\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p&gt;老婆每年蒐集Georg Jensen的年度項鍊系列，每年都去sogo專櫃，今天陪老婆第一次去了新光三越A8的專櫃。專櫃小姐很親切，很耐心說明。也有建議給我老婆很時尚的搭配的方式。\r\n重點是今天的專櫃小姐對自己的產品系列的歷史很瞭解。非常可信可靠。過去幾年的設計款式，特點，顏色通通都記得。非常專業。推薦！\r\n                    &lt;/p&gt;                    \r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                &lt;div class=\"image-block\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;img src=\"{{media url=wysiwyg/testimonial/as.jpeg}}\" alt=\"\" /&gt;\r\n                    &lt;span class=\"testimonial-name\"&gt;林玉幼&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                    &lt;span class=\"testimonial-desc\"&gt;Fashion Designer&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n            &lt;/div&gt;\r\n        &lt;/div&gt;\r\n        &lt;script&gt;\r\n            require([\'jquery\', \'apparelowlcarousel\'], function() {\r\n                jQuery(document).ready(function() {\r\n                    jQuery(\".testimonial-slider\").owlCarousel({\r\n                        items: 1,\r\n                        itemsDesktop: [1199, 1],\r\n                        itemsDesktopSmall: [991, 1],\r\n                        itemsTablet: [767, 1],\r\n                        itemsTabletSmall: [639, 1],\r\n                        itemsMobile: [479, 1],\r\n                        pagination: false,\r\n                        navigationText: [\"&lt;div class=\'prev-arrow\'&gt;&lt;i class=\'fa fa-angle-left\'&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\", \"&lt;div class=\'next-arrow\'&gt;&lt;i class=\'fa fa-angle-right\'&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\"],\r\n                        navigation: true,\r\n                        autoPlay: true,\r\n                    });\r\n                    jQuery(\".testimonial-slider .item\").show();\r\n                });\r\n            });\r\n        &lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;</div>','2024-12-19 08:26:50','2024-12-21 09:40:23',1),
